OL,3,CPeston: Why wasn't Kaddour-Cherif
OL,4,Cdeported?
OL,6,FThe point, I am told, is that none of
OL,7,Fhis sentences met the threshold for
OL,8,Fautomatic deportation, namely a 12-
OL,9,Fmonth or longer custodial sentence.
OL,11,FEven so, initial deportation
OL,12,Fproceedings - or what's known as a
OL,13,Fstage one notification - were taken
OL,14,Fagainst him earlier this year.
OL,16,FThat is because his repeat offending
OL,17,Fhistory was seen as contrary to the
OL,18,Fpublic good.
