OL,3,CPeston: Why wasn't Kaddour-Cherif
OL,4,Cdeported?
OL,6,FEven if he is found, it is not clear
OL,7,Fwhether even then he would be deported.
OL,9,FThis is messy, to put it mildly.
OL,11,FOne big question is why someone who
OL,12,Fhas overstayed their visa entitlement
OL,13,Fwould not be automatically deported
OL,14,Fwhen put on the sex offender register?
OL,16,FWithin government, the mess is causing
OL,17,Fwhat you might call cross-departmental
OL,18,Fconsternation.
